reviewText: This DVD has great easy to make recipes.  Food Network should be ashamed they took her off the air because she was the only reason I watched.  #TeamPaula

My daughter loves Paula Dean so this was a gift and she loves it!
Set of 3 DVDs great value!

I love Paula and the interesting things she is cooking on this video.  She is a wonderful cook, and I have learned so much by her showing her techniques and her family recipes.  This is a great video, and I am so glad that Amazon had it for me to order.  Thanks so much, Amazon for having Paula Deen videos.
even though this is an older show, it has so much paula dean style. the recipes are easy and so down home good
